The pattern has a seamless layout, meaning that the edges of the design blend together seamlessly to create a continuous and uninterrupted pattern.

The pink and green colors used in the pattern evoke a sense of tropical warmth and relaxation, making it perfect for use in beach-themed or vacation-related designs.
